<lb n="0346a26"/>傳教大師<anchor id="fxT21p0346a05"/>臣法天奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0346a27"/><p>次下諸部真言。請召發遣供獻加持並皆通
<lb n="0346a28"/>用</p>
<lb n="0346a29"/><p type="dharani">阿難哆&CB00425;納摩<note place="inline">二合引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1283.0346b" n="0346b"/>
<lb n="0346b01"/><p>此是蓮花寶藏真言</p>
<lb n="0346b02"/><p type="dharani">阿難哆商佉<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0346b03"/><p>此是硨磲寶藏真言</p>
