<lb n="0349a04"/>引</note>賀烏里馱<note place="inline">二合</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>尼娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0349a05"/>賀冒吠<note place="inline">引</note>瑟拏<note place="inline">二合</note>尾<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀阿尾挽帝
<lb n="0349a06"/>迦<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>護哆<note place="inline">引</note>娑曩<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0349a07"/>野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀設訖帝<note place="inline">二合</note>摩寫<note place="inline">引</note>摩<note place="inline">引</note>野娑&CB00085;
