<lb n="0349a09"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>賀&CB00085;嚕拏哆摩里&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0349a10"/>賀播<note place="inline">引</note>世<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>普敢<note place="inline">二合</note>惹曩野娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二
